description:
South Bank hotel with free breakfast near Waterloo Station

Near the London Eye

Located on the south side of the Thames, Hampton by Hilton London Waterloo is a 5-minute stroll from the Waterloo train and underground station. You can walk 10 minutes to the South Bank Center, London Eye, or SEA LIFE London Aquarium.

Shakespeare's Globe

There’s plenty to do in this south London area, with the Tate Modern art gallery, Royal National Theatre, and Globe Theatre within easy reach. You can get to London’s other top attractions, like the British Museum and National Gallery, from Waterloo Underground Station.

24-hour refreshments

Each morning you’ll be treated to a free hot breakfast, while a restaurant and coffee shop are available throughout the day. You can use the free fitness room during your stay, and the multilingual staff can help you navigate the city and book tickets for shows.

Free WiFi

After a day exploring the city, you can curl up in front of the flat-screen LCD TV or connect to the free WiFi. All of the hotel’s air-conditioned rooms come with an armchair or sofa bed, a laptop-size safe, and tea and coffee making facilities. Daily housekeeping is offered.

HOTEL_AMENITY.value:
Dining options at the hotel include a restaurant, a coffee shop/café, and a snack bar/deli. A complimentary breakfast is offered. High-speed wireless Internet access is complimentary. Business-related amenities at this 3-star property consist of a 24-hour business center and a meeting room. 4 meeting rooms are available. This business-friendly hotel also offers a fitness center, tour/ticket assistance, and multilingual staff.

Hampton by Hilton London Waterloo is a smoke-free property.
